_length": 113, "reply_to": 862554894, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774595060}, {"pid": 862556391, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 54, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-27 15:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "国算我就不漏我自己做什么了 我最近运气不好。红内裤都挡不住  就不连累大家了 <br/><br/>MD 减持  我都不懂为什么会挑那个时候发。", "lou": 1562, "content_length": 106, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774595660}, {"pid": 862556862, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-27 15:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862556640,45974302,3096]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67138111]Altyport[/uid] (2026-03-27 15:16):[/b]<br/><br/>主要是被某队搞的心乱了，操作变形了[s:a2:lucky][/quote]<br/>我操作没有变形 但是我扛不住雷劈 而且我很小心了  没有靠近大树还是被劈到了", "lou": 1563, "content_length": 73, "reply_to": 862556640, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774595883}, {"pid": 862557173, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 89, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-27 15:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862556881,45974302,3096]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-03-27 15:18):[/b]<br/><br/>本命年吗狼大？ 你不会比我大一轮吧？[/quote]<br/>这还用本命年？你问哪个炒股的不是天天红内裤的？涨的时候一条穿几天都不洗  跌的时候天天换。", "lou": 1564, "content_length": 91, "reply_to": 862556881, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774596022}, {"pid": 862570894, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-27 17:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862569274,45974302,3102]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-03-27 16:58):[/b]<br/><br/>这里不是底，我只是割在相对底部吧。&amp;#160; 不割的话等真底部我又没钱加仓。[s:ac:哭笑]<br/><br/>既然狼大判断是绞肉机，那就按绞肉机来做， 冲高就卖， 下杀就买， 不重仓。<br/><br/><br/>满仓仙人已经盖牌认输 ，谁接替我的位置吧。[/quote]<br/>我都不懂你听到哪去  我说深套的 躺到哪个位置减仓 特别是你这种科技ETF的 你再回去看一下", "lou": 1565, "content_length": 84, "reply_to": 862569274, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774602804}, {"pid": 862572716, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-27 17:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862571113,45974302,3103]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-03-27 17:15):[/b]<br/><br/>没套， 我ETF没亏。。。。 就是降低仓位，不那么重了。&amp;#160;&amp;#160;<br/><br/>ETF我算是平出。[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>反正下周半导体材料带ETF上去你不要认错追高就行", "lou": 1566, "content_length": 50, "reply_to": 862571113, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774603818}, {"pid": 862576510, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 31, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-27 18:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们还记得我之前对原油的判断么  还没签完单子 没那么快结束的 现在不是只有川普要卖油了  利益扩大化了", "lou": 1567, "content_length": 92, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774605986}, {"pid": 862817570, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 09:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862816523,45974302,3125]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=331181]xhox[/uid] (2026-03-30 09:52):[/b]<br/><br/>缩量涨，放量跌，是何意味[s:ac:汗]<br/><br/>观察10点~10点半是否最低点[/quote]<br/>每天都有一点融资盘爆掉，其他的都死扛，这里没人愿意主动杀跌 都是扛不住就爆了的那种。所以是每天早盘脉冲式放量。", "lou": 1568, "content_length": 113, "reply_to": 862816523, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774835967}, {"pid": 862818382, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 10:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862817076,45974302,3125]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66747163]learla[/uid] (2026-03-30 09:56):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，3900收费站马上要降到3850收费站了[/quote]<br/>放心  暂时还没到最后的C 现在还是B反 目前还是3900收费站区间。<br/>我目前在做细分题材。局部行情。", "lou": 1569, "content_length": 91, "reply_to": 862817076, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774836280}, {"pid": 862821568, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 10:24", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862820939,45974302,3128]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60608517]Jerowe[/uid] (2026-03-30 10:19):[/b]<br/><br/>是不是在再升[/quote]<br/>我现在点票我觉得真是害人 不开玩笑<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202603/30/jmQ2x-e18lK6T1kS9v-1a.jpg[/img]<br/>比如现在 我就是在害人", "lou": 1570, "content_length": 94, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202603/30/jmQ2x-e18lK6T1kS9v-1a.jpg", "size": 6, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202603/30", "name": "jmQ2x-e18lK6T1kS9v-1a.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 862820939, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774837446}, {"pid": 862822096, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 10:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我自己做好我的几个细分就行了 我做的都是资金面的  一个是国算 一个是商航  纯资金面博弈<br/>就是赌他们自救和做主反。<br/>消息面有催化 基本面不爆雷是前提", "lou": 1571, "content_length": 132, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774837647}, {"pid": 862822240, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 10:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862821953,45974302,3128]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65610553]来一份甜辣的甜不辣[/uid] (2026-03-30 10:26):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大我真在里面[s:ac:咦][/quote]<br/>伸头一刀 缩头也是一刀 去哪不是被割", "lou": 1572, "content_length": 37, "reply_to": 862821953, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774837701}, {"pid": 862822564, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 5, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 10:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862822391,45974302,3129]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60608517]Jerowe[/uid] (2026-03-30 10:29):[/b]<br/><br/>就是做spacex相关的咯[s:ac:茶][/quote]<br/>对 就6个票  多一个都不看", "lou": 1573, "content_length": 26, "reply_to": 862822391, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774837820}, {"pid": 862823072, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 13, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 10:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862822515,45974302,3129]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42051801]skwh[/uid] (2026-03-30 10:29):[/b]<br/><br/>乐，狼大还正在做这个，我就说很熟悉[/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202603/30/jmQ2x-f1xgKaT1kSfa-1i.jpg[/img]<br/>这个是不是更熟悉", "lou": 1574, "content_length": 58, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202603/30/jmQ2x-f1xgKaT1kSfa-1i.jpg", "size": 10, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202603/30", "name": "jmQ2x-f1xgKaT1kSfa-1i.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 862822515, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774837997}, {"pid": 862823181, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 9, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 10:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862822983,45974302,3129]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41288139]霍华德李[/uid] (2026-03-30 10:32):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 帮我问下 ywk 主力，最近是不是休息中[/quote]<br/>大票目前没办法 等2.5WE再说", "lou": 1575, "content_length": 30, "reply_to": 862822983, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774838035}, {"pid": 862823239, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 7, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-30 10:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862823084,45974302,3129]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60859666]Boom_Panda[/uid] (2026-03-30 10:33):[/b]<br/><br/>再升 西部 信维 通宇 天银吗  还有个是什么 超捷？[/quote]<br/>西侧", "lou": 1576, "content_length": 9, "reply_to": 862823084, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774838056}, {"pid": 862823936, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "a